AN ACT CONCERNING CHARTER SCHOOLS AND EDUCATIONAL
OPPORTUNITIES.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 That section 10-66ee of the general statutes be amended to adjust
2 funding for state and local charter schools.
Statement of Purpose:
To improve educational opportunities for students by adjusting funding
for charter schools.
